{
  "arquivo": "ca04_14",
  "total": 84,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(What, nobody's here yet?\\n It's about time to gather, though...\\n Well, it's not like we have to be punctual.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But...seriously now, what's going on...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Well, I should calm down and think.\\n First, Nino and Miku.\\n There's definitely something weird about them.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(They're like, strangely active, aren't they?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's just like last summer...\\n Back then, those two...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(No way. It's happening again...?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But, why now? They both know\\n that I confessed to Yotsuba and we're dating.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Plus, after the confession,\\n those two talked it over in their own way%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Well, Nino was saying something dangerous,\\n but that was probably her way of encouraging Yotsuba.\\n I wonder if she was serious...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(But, Ichika and Itsuki are also acting suspicious.\\n They probably know something.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(However, I don't think those two \\n would tell me so easily.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Good grief...\\n they're as annoying as ever.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun, I found you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You're here already.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Good timing.\\nThere's something I want to ask you guys.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Huh? What is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, it's about your attitude towards me.\\nAre you hiding something from me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Why do you ask?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You've been weirdly clinging to me since this\\nmorning, and you're being oddly active...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, you're just being self-conscious.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, we're just being our usual selves.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yep. Normal.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What do you mean?\\nYou guys aren't usually like this.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, you've been busy studying for exams,\\nso you haven't been paying attention to us.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's...probably true.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "And also, maybe we're just feeling\\nmore free and relaxed on this trip.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I wouldn't mind if you pay more attention to me,\\nFu-kun.\\nActually, I'd be ecstatic if you did.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nah, I can't do that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "What's the issue?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well I mean, I already%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba and the others sure are late.\\nThe meeting time has already passed, hasn't it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "What should we do?\\nShould we go ahead, just the three of us?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, that's%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WOAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Well, if it isn't Yotsuba.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Y-Yotsuba?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?\\nU-um, well...this is...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's this all the sudden?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I-I wonder.\\nAhaha...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Bad big bro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Raiha?\\nIchika and Itsuki too...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "If you suddenly raise your voice,\\neven Yotsuba-san will be surprised, won't she?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ahh...\\nSorry, Yotsuba.\\nI startled you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I'm the one who's sorry...\\nfor doing something so weird.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "It's not weird.\\nNo, it's okay. It's normal for two people\\nin love to link arms, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah, that's right.\\nThat's the standard.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, come on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ummm... Then, please excuse me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Yep yep, you two did great.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...\\nI-in that case, let's go to the next place.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's wrong? Did something happen?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?!\\nN-no, nothing really...\\nSorry, I ended up running without realizing it...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha, sorry. I surprised you,\\ndidn't I? We'll move away right away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "N-no, it's okay. There's no need to move away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Because, you know.\\nWe're, um...together.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wh-what?\\nI'm just speaking the truth.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah.\\nTh-...that's right, yes.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It's okay for two people in love\\nto do something like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ichika?\\nRaiha and Itsuki...you're here too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...\\nI-in that case, let's go to the next place.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You can stay like that, you know.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "...Eh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "But...um...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's not weird or anything.\\nI mean, we're...dating.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Well, that's true.\\nBut, everyone is here, so...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I...don't really mind.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, you know.\\nIf you don't mind, that is?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Um...\\nI...I'm okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Raiha",
      "texto_en": "Since you two are a couple,\\nit's only natural to do this kind of thing!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Raiha?\\nIchika and Itsuki...you're here too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...\\nI-in that case, let's go to the next place.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*\\nI was really worried\\nwhen Yotsuba suddenly started running like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "But this is beyond our expectations, right?\\nThis plan was super effective.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I've never seen Yotsuba's face like that before.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "She's got a little fire in her too, doesn't she.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ooohh...\\nI hope nothing else happens from now on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}